TextEng: I'm very sorry. What is your name?
My apologies. Mind if I ask you some questions?
You look like you are having a rough day. Why don't you tell me your name?
Text: 힘든 하루인 것 같네. 이름이 뭐야?

TextEng: Could you answer some questions?
What's your name?
Yeah, whatever. I have a question.
No be 'fraid. Who you be?
No be scared. Me have questions.
Goodbye.
They call me <FirstName>.
My name is <FullName>. But please just call me <FirstName>. It is a pleasure to meet you Jaheel.
Text: 내 이름은 <FullName>야. 그냥 <FirstName>라고 불러. 만나서 반가워 자힐.

TextEng: My name isn't important right now.
Me is <FirstName>.
Me called <FullName>. But you call me <FirstName>. I glad meet you.
You no ask name. You not need know.
Text: 이름 물어봐도 안 돼. 알 필요 없어.

TextEng: What's so terrible about today?
I wish I could help you, but I am in need of a job. Do you know of anything?
Text: 도와주고 싶지만 나도 일자리가 필요해. 뭐 아는 거 있어?

TextEng: I am hunting the cult that started the plague in Neverwinter. Have you heard anything about them?
Text: 네버윈터에 역병을 퍼뜨린 사교를 쫓고 있어. 뭐 들은 거 있어?

TextEng: I'd love to hear about your troubles, but just now I need some directions.
Text: 사정을 듣고 싶지만 지금은 길 좀 알아야 해.

TextEng: You know stuff 'bout cult that start bad plague in Neverwinter, maybe?
Text: 네버윈터에 나쁜 역병 퍼뜨린 사교 알아?

TextEng: Me need good job.
You no whine! You help me find stuff.
Text: 징징대지 마! 나 찾는 거 도와줘.

TextEng: Oh lady, why so sad?
I am sorry your day is so dark. Might I ask for your name?
Who you?
What troubles are those?
Why do you think the bandits took him captive?
Do you know where the bandits took him?
Are you offering a reward for his rescue?
I would love to rescue him for you.
That's rough, but I'm not really interested in getting my throat slit by a gang of thugs. Goodbye.
Text: 안됐지만 깡패들한테 목 따이긴 싫어. 잘 있어.

TextEng: Why bad guys keep brother?
Where they take brother?
You pay for rescue maybe?
Me tough guy, me rescue brother!
Me too busy for rescue. You find someone else.
Text: 나 너무 바빠. 다른 사람 찾아.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Do you think I might be able to get an advance on that reward? To help me buy supplies for a rescue?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 보상 일부 먼저 받을 수 있어? 구출 준비물 사야 해서.

TextEng: I'll do it, but words don't have any value. I want some gold up front to prove you have any. Now lady!
Text: 해줄게, 하지만 말로는 안 돼. 금화 있다는 걸 증명해. 당장!

TextEng: I will do my best.
Neva is as good as rescued. Do not worry, my lady.
Text: 네바는 구한 거나 마찬가지야. 걱정 마.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me need gold first, please.
Me no think you have reward. You pay some now to show.
Text: 나 네가 보상 있다고 안 믿어. 지금 좀 줘봐.

TextEng: Me go try best.
Neva be safe soon. Me get him.
I can't remember where you said that stone formation was.
Not yet, but I'm working on it.
Don't rush me. I'll save him eventually.
Me forget where Ninvi... er... Nivi... where brother be.
Text: 나 닌비... 어... 니비... 오빠 어디 있는지 까먹었어.

TextEng: No, but me working on it.
Me do soon, or maybe later.
Tell me where he can be found.
You tell me where he be.
Not yet, but I'm working on it.
Just be patient. I'll get to it in good time.
Text: 조금만 기다려. 때 되면 할 거야.

TextEng: No, but me working on it.
Me do soon, or maybe not.
Text: 나 곧 해, 아니면 안 할지도.

TextEng: No I am not with <CUSTOM1001>.
Yes, I'm with <CUSTOM1001>.
Me not with <CUSTOM1001>.
Yep - me with <CUSTOM1001>.
Why don't you tell me about your troubles, so that I can assist you.
Text: 무슨 걱정인지 말해봐, 도와줄 수 있으니까.

TextEng: Me help, if you tell what me do.
Text: 나 도와줘, 뭐 하면 되는지 말해줘.

TextEng: Why do you think the bandits took him captive?
Do you know where the bandits took him?
Are you offering a reward for his rescue?
I would love to rescue him for you.
That's rough, but I'm not really interested in getting my throat slit by a gang of thugs. Goodbye.
Text: 안됐지만 깡패들한테 목 따이긴 싫어. 잘 있어.

TextEng: Why bad guys keep brother?
Where they take brother?
You pay for rescue maybe?
Me tough, me rescue brother!
Me too busy for rescue. You find someone else.
Text: 나 너무 바빠. 다른 사람 찾아.
